    INSERT INTO story(id, title, issue_id, synopsis, reprint_notes, notes, type_id) VALUES(52784,"In Pluto's Kingdom Part 1: The Secret of the Dark Planet", 4922,"After a Holliday girl is abducted by King Pluto Wonder Woman and the Holliday girls travel to the furthest planet where the king extracts their \"color bodies\" to light his gloomy planet and attempts to melt Wonder Woman like a color tablet.",NULL,"Writer credit from The Secret History of Wonder Woman (Jill Lapore 2014) also confirmed to Jerry Bails.Joye Hummel is the maiden name for the scripter (before 1947) then she married David Murchison. When he passed away Joye married Jack Kelly. So her name all combined reads Joye Hummel Murchison Kelly the way Jill Lapore refers to her in her book above.According to Hippolyte the River Styx is actually the stream of interplanetary ether between Earth and Pluto. This story was written when Pluto was still considered a planet not a dwarf planet.  Wonder Woman travels through space dragged behind a rocket ship holding her breath; luckily there's oxygen on Pluto.",19
